<item>
 <title>Overview</title>
 <link>https://amboyna.org/overview</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-date field--type-text field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Date:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Overview &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Body:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;startblock&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although Amboyna remained controversial for centuries, the trial itself took place over just 15 days in February and March 1623.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This timeline allows you to explore what happened day-by-day. Click on the individual names to see each of the confessions and the final bloody resolution of the trial. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-confession field--type-image field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Confession:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://amboyna.org/sites/default/files/timeline/timelinecollage.jpg&quot; width=&quot;1148&quot; height=&quot;800&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
